p: The EO of Cupressus macrocarpa branchlets contains 19 compounds (Table 1). The major chemical constituents identified included terpinen-4-ol (23.7%), α-phellandrene (19.2%), α-citronellol (17.3%), citronellal (6.6%), D-camphor (5.4%), γ-terpinene (5.3%), α-terpinene (3.08%), α-myrcene (2.2%), limonene (2.16%), α-terpineol (1.7%), terpinolene (1.8%), and α-linalool (1.5%).
